{
  "stem": "26142.10",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I forgot to say what is said-- what we had to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had to get out from this mikvah place, cross a river into another forest that was called [INAUDIBLE], go two and a half kilometers inside the forest, then recross the river again and cross the highway and go into the other side of the highway.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That forest is called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we are to be on top there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "From there, we can see any car coming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When the car will come, then we descend down there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We get in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We did remember that crossing that-- that river, that there was a small [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] pedestrian bridge.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "A little-- a few hundred meters below, there was a regular bridge that-- that wagons and trucks could go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But we didn't want to cross it with that bridge.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Fortunately, we remembered that there is a small-- a small that what's called a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We will go over there, and we came, and we found it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was still there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we managed to-- to get across.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the way the instructions were, we met on that side of the mountain two kilometers down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We knew the area well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And so we came to that place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we sat there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we waited for that-- for that to come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "That detective came in time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we-- we saw he turned around, and he flashed-- turned the lights off and on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we descended the mountain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we got into the car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we had 20 kilometers to the-- to the-- to [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Wolow. ?] That place had to be-- it was a dangerous point to cross.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Because [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Wolow ?] was only 25 kilometers from the border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And over there, every car, every truck, was-- was checkpoints.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
